title: Don’t Forget To Remember // Fun Month at TC(Week 2)Pastor Robert Madu
description: If you have ever forgotten about what God has done in your life, this message is a perfect reminder for you! Pastor Robert Madu spoke today about the seasons of breaking and how they are not meant to break you, but instead prepare you for the MORE God has for you! “How many loaves do you have?” Don’t know what we are talking about? Listen to this message to find out!
